.Dd May 17, 2026
.Dt VERYDYNAMICWINDOWMANAGER 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm verydynamicwindowmanager
.Nd DOOMSDAY window-manager module
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is the named DOOMSDAY module for
.Xr vdwm 1 ,
the custom dynamic X11 window manager build. The installer pairs it with
DoomMenu because the desktop workflow expects both the window manager and menu
launcher.
.Sh INSTALL
.Dl \&./install.sh --wm
.Sh INSTALLED COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width "vdwm"
.It Nm vdwm
Window manager executable.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr doomsday-system 1 ,
.Xr doommenu 1 ,
.Xr vdwm 1
